{"tid":646586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔有無諗過好多南亞裔人士努力工作為香港作出貢獻","createTime":"2018-04-29T07:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T05:52:25.000Z","uid":177244,"like":14,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b44368ae20a38c282f1a362e7aa30bda215a5eb1","tid":646586,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"有d連登仔成日睇唔起南亞人，有無諗過佢地幾積極就業、融入社會，同時因為文化差異、語言隔閡而處處踫壁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最初印度人隨英國佬黎香港做生意，有d過黎當兵、做警察。佢地保衛香港、除暴安良嗰時連登仔都未出世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勞動人口參與率男性有79.9%，女性有51.2%；合計65.6%（全港男性68.1%，女性54.8%，合計61.1%）<br />\n南亞裔人士37.6%從事較高技術職位，淨計印度人更加有64.9%（全港則有40.8%）<br />\n在職人士月入中位數印度人$22000，全港$15500<br />\n公屋住戶只有14.4%，65.5%同大家一樣比緊私樓貴租<br />\n30%香港出世<br />\n38.1%有專上學歷<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以從以下資料瞭解下南亞裔人士生活情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.povertyrelief.gov.hk/pdf/Hong%20Kong%20Poverty%20Situation%20Report%20on%20Ethnic%20Minorities%202016_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.povertyrelief.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FHong%2520Kong%2520Poverty%2520Situation%2520Report%2520on%2520Ethnic%2520Minorities%25202016_chi.pdf&d=o8%2BTk3IUjjEpsGaWMkGHBJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=ffb1226d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.povertyrelief.gov.hk/pdf/Hong%20Kong%20Poverty%20Situation%20Report%20on%20Ethnic%20Minorities%202016_chi.pdf</a><br />\n2016年香港少數族裔人士貧窮情況報告<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/hc/sub_com/hs52/papers/hs52_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr16-17%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fsub_com%2Fhs52%2Fpapers%2Fhs52_c.htm&d=o8%2BTk3IUjjEpsGaWMkGHBJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=c4cd390f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/hc/sub_com/hs52/papers/hs52_c.htm</a><br />\n少數族裔權益事宜小組委員會 (文件)"},{"pid":"af81e1e2e4bcde15f9d96640a4ce8a70408f4d19","tid":646586,"uid":177244,"like